  "text": "Bayesian network meta-analysis was performed to synthesize the results of the included studies simultaneously regarding change from baseline in FEV 1 and the transitional dyspnea index total score at 12 weeks to obtain relative efficacy estimates for indacaterol 75 µg versus FOR/BUD, SAL/FP, and placebo. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] A Bayesian network meta-analysis includes data, a likelihood distribution, a model with parameters, and prior distributions. [CITATION_4] The model links the data from the individual studies to basic parameters, which represent the (pooled) relative treatment effect of each treatment versus placebo.",
